  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you'll have a great selection at the buffet breakfast including fruit, cereal, bread, jams, ham and cheese, pastries and more.</p>
<p>Dinner is three courses with choices and each Thursday the hotel hosts a typical Trentino dinner which is a great opportunity to try some local dishes from the region. Choose a wine from the hotel's extensive wine list to enjoy with your meal.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
