  <description><![CDATA[<p>Run by the Cozzini family, the Hotel Ideal has a really welcoming atmosphere and spacious alpine style rooms. The family have put a lot of effort into renovating the spa so you can spend some time winding down after a day exploring. What's more they use as much renewable energy as they can in the running of the hotel, making it a more sustainable choice!</p>
<h2>Great for active families </h2>
<p>With rooms sleeping up to four people available, children and families are welcome at the Hotel Ideal. The hotel's also within easy walking distance to lifts that'll hike you up to walking trails and fantastic viewpoints. This is a great hotel for families who want to spend all their time outdoors and want easy access to the local amenities.</p>]]></description>
